freetext.SYMPTOMS_DESCRIPTION: I have blisters all inside my mouth for about 5 days. They are painful and annoying.  Ive never had this before. Ive been gargling with hot water and salt.
I think I told you about blisters in my mouth. I still have soreness on my tongue and inside my mouth.

freetext.SYSTEMIC_REACTION_OTHER: I forgot the first couple of days I had really scary nightmares. Also, right after the 2nd, I had so much energy... washed floors, etc. I still have more energy than before!
I had hives on both shoulders and upper back last night. Its ok now.
My dry mouth continues. I dont know if its from the vaccine but I never had it before:
